Todo list React JS Project

JSX-- Javascript Syntax Extension
--JSX use to insert JS dynamically with html

--index.js  -entry point of js

App.js --main component

Components in React 
1. class based
2. function based

**
Adding Bootstrap in React-
-add cdn in app/index.html

Creating Components
-make a folder e.g - src/MyComponents
-component's name should be start with capital letter. e.g : Header.js

How to include components in App.js?
e.g :  <Header></Header>
e.g : 

Props in react :
//default proptypes -- if you not provide any props it will display default props
Header.defaultProps = {
    title: "Your Title Here"
} ---in header.js

//proptypes --
Header.propTypes = {        
    title: PropTypes.string
}

How to add style? in react
    let footerStyle = {
        position: "absolute",
        top: "100vh",
        width: "100%"
    }
    <header style={footerStyle}>
    //you can pass variable like this



